{"tid":1590491,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好自責自己做唔到前線","createTime":"2019-09-23T17:41:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T20:35:47.000Z","uid":233118,"like":72,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"3b674100cf372542e6685541e722d734a8565466","tid":1590491,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:41:18.000Z","msg":"發夢雖然都叫前，但未真喺去到面對面對打咁前，次次都就嚟出事就走<br />\n<br />\n小弟心態喺以武抗暴，汽油彈當常態，吊死警犬拍手掌嘅人<br />\n<br />\n奈何內心真係有恐懼感，次次都克服唔到<br />\n<br />\n見到前線咁搏，又見到前線比人打，真係好心痛，之後就開始怪責自己點解無勇氣去現場幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真喺好撚痛苦"},{"pid":"08139bda3f0e1c1a1845fffa4b54d22c9242be9e","tid":1590491,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:41:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"12fc302d82bfccf012239b66a86bf7789e23f072","tid":1590491,"uid":233118,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:41:46.000Z","msg":"請善用不推文回覆"},{"pid":"882df3af8d405cdf4c2cb8cb2c4ac9d44edcf44f","tid":1590491,"uid":233118,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:43:09.000Z","msg":"純粹發泄吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟明白自己定位喺邊<br />\n但真心覺得自己好無力"},{"pid":"f1b40b94e5ae757cd4ab22ad70a5e028d0a233d6","tid":1590491,"uid":179225,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:49:31.000Z","msg":"同你一樣都係內心勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行唔到上去， 咪係其他方面做多D 野囉"},{"pid":"26a2cf0633f3c4af161d07eea6a99b4c6edd91df","tid":1590491,"uid":134099,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"882df3af8d405cdf4c2cb8cb2c4ac9d44edcf44f","tid":1590491,"uid":233118,"like":1,"dislike":1,